Galaga 
Requirements:
score is determined by destroying alien ships
score is incremented by 5 for small ships, 10 for large (boss) ships
ships must descend (potentially zig and zag)
user can orient their ship by moving left and right
there is no time limit
background must have twinkling stars
user can customize their ship (color or alternate ship options)
alien ships must be discernable (different from the user)
user lasers are green
alien lasers are red
lives are displayed top-left
score is displayed top-right
time is displayed top-center
alien ships appear in waves
menu displays "Play", "Options", "Quit" and a leaderboard
leaderboard is displayeds below "Quit" and scores are in descending order
background on menu screen must also have twinkling stars
user can edit ship in "Options"
once a user dies; display time, score and a death message
